nal-link" href=3D"https://one.dev1.ui.westpac.com.au/npm/docs/ui-framework/=
1.7.3/core/api-client/index.html" rel=3D"nofollow">ApiClient<span>&nbsp;</s=
pan></a>helper will inject this header; it will always "Internal" for UI ca=
lling the Experience API.</p><p>enum:<br>
