<h3 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-3.3.ExtractingAccountIDs">3.3. Extracting Acco=
unt IDs</h3>
<p>List of accounts should be stored in a Mesh secret and to be retrieved i=
n the runtime.</p>
<p><strong style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);letter-spacing: 0.0px;">&nbsp;:i=
nformation: <strong><a href=3D"#expgalaxypaymentv2-top">Go to top of this p=
age</a></strong></strong></p>
<p><br></p>
<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-4.1Capability:Initiatingapayment">4.1 Capabili=
ty: Initiating a payment</h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-POST/paymentCreate">POST /paymentCreate</h2>
<p>This endpoint submits a payment order to <a href=3D"/display/ARTC/Paymen=
t+Initiation+API+v1.0">Payment Initiation API v1.0</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><u><strong>FEB 2026 Changes:&nbsp;<=
/strong></u></span></p>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">As part of Payment Initiation CAP API V2 cha=
nges, Channels is expected to submit(POST) the payment to V2 version of the=
 API(<a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/cap-prodsvcfulf=
lmnt-pymntprocsng-pymntinit-v2" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">ht=
tps://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/cap-prodsvcfulflmnt-pymntprocsng-=
pymntinit-v2</a>) instead of V1 version. The changes will be applicable in =
this endpoint(Payments EXP API POST /payments) and the corresponding code c=
hanges will be applicable in the "<strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,7=
7);">postPaymentsController.helper.ts</span></strong>" EXP API component to=
 handle the following,</p>
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li>EXP API request to CAP API request mapping, the code changes will be re=
quired in the<span>&nbsp;</span><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://=
bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/WDP/repos/galaxy-payment-microfronten=
d/browse/api/server/api/helpers/postPaymentsController.helper.ts#84" rel=3D=
"nofollow">generatePaymentsRequestDataForCAP</a><span>&nbsp;</span>function=
.</li>
<li>CAP API response to EXP API response mapping, the code changes will be =
required in the&nbsp;<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://bitbucket.s=
rv.westpac.com.au/projects/WDP/repos/galaxy-payment-microfrontend/browse/ap=
i/server/api/helpers/postPaymentsController.helper.ts#12" rel=3D"nofollow">=
transformPaymentsResponseFromCAPToUI</a><span>&nbsp;</span>function.</li>
</ul>
<p>Refer to the following Mapping details section in the SD here for mappin=
g details that are applicable as part of this change: <a href=3D"/display/A=
RTC/Channels+SD+%3A+Payment+Initiation+CAP+API+-V1+to+V2+upgrade#ChannelsSD=
:PaymentInitiationCAPAPIV1toV2upgrade-EXPAPItoPaymentInitiationV2CAPAPIMapp=
ing">Channels SD : Payment Initiation CAP API -V1 to V2 upgrade#EXPAPItoPay=
mentInitiationV2CAPAPIMapping</a></p>
<p>Also, as part of the request body, following request attributes will be =
included/added under <strong>supplementaryData</strong>. These will mapped =
with the values based on the aliasLookup response that gets called in make =
a payment page.</p>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">aliasResolutionTime</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,8=
1);">aliasRegistrationTime</span></span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,8=
1);">aliasLastUpdateTime</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81=
);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><u><strong>May 2026 ERM changes as=
sociated with Confirmation of Payee:</strong></u></span><span style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(23,43,77);"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,=
0,0);">As part of CoP feature, if CoP validation is performed by a maker wh=
en initiating a payment to a new beneficiary, the CoP validation matched st=
atus Outcome should be included as part of the "supplementaryData" in the E=
XP API request so that the CoP validation outcome can be displayed in the p=
ayments details authorisation screen. Refer to the SD here for details:</sp=
an><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><a href=
=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/06+-+SD%3A+Confirmat=
ion+of+payee#id-06SD:Confirmationofpayee-Sequenceflowdiagram" rel=3D"nofoll=
ow">06 - SD: Confirmation of payee - Sequenceflowdiagram</a></span></span><=
/p>
