gn: left;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><strong>Pattern</strong>: ^(\=
d{11})$<br>
 This is an organisation CIS Key</span></p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><=
span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><strong>Note</strong>:<br>
 This header is used to send the query parameter organisation CIS Key. This=
 header is provided as an alternative standard in the event that an API nee=
ds to handle PII within the URI. More info<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=3D"htt=
ps://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/MESH/Pattern+19%3A+API+Endpoint+=
Design+Patterns#Pattern19:APIEndpointDesignPatterns-Pattern19.3.5-UsingHead=
