<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-POST/paymentCreateForNewBeneficiaryFEB26"><spa=
n>POST /<span data-teams=3D"true">paymentCreateForNewBeneficiary</span></sp=
an><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current conf-macro o=
utput-inline" style=3D"color: rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration: none;" data=
-hasbody=3D"false" data-macro-name=3D"status">FEB26</span></h2>
<p>This endpoint submits a payment order to&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://conflue=
nce.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/Payment+Initiation+API+v1.0" rel=3D"nof=
ollow">Payment Initiation API v1.0</a><span>&nbsp;</span>(only for the user=
s who gets Payment to new beneficiary permutations)</p>
