<h3 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-6.3.ResponseFiltering"><span style=3D"font-siz=
e: 16.0px;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: -0.006em;">6.3. Response Filter=
ing</span></h3>
<p>UI should filter the API response based on user role using Tactical Solu=
tion for Entitlements to Authorise users; refer to it solution design here:=
 &nbsp;<a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/jXbHYg" class=3D"=
" rel=3D"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/jXbHYg</a></p>
<h3 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-6.4DownstreamAPIInfo">6.4 <span style=3D"font-=
size: 16.0px;letter-spacing: -0.006em;">Downstream API Info</span></h3>
<p>This endpoint will consume the following PDP query API.</p>
<ul>
<li>PDPQueryAPI : GetDivisionsFromPdpQueryResult</li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">PDPQueryAPI request:&nbsp;</span></l=
i>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "query": [
        {
            "attribute": "RequestAttributes.DivisionId"
        }
    ],
    "context": {
        "action": "QUERY",
        "attributes": {
            "RequestAttributes.CustomerUserId": "07a975e0-0a90-4e1c-96d1-c2=
a1e5dcc5a2",
            "RequestAttributes.OrganisationId": "32896172",
            "RequestAttributes.RequestAction": "VIEW_ACCOUNT"
        }
    }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">PDPQueryAPI response:</span>
<ul>
<li>PDP query response to EXP API mapping=20
<ul>
<li>divisionId =3D results[i].value</li>
<li>divisionName =3D results[i].statements[0].payload=E2=86=92 map the "nam=
e" attribute within the payload</li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "requestId": "c7b2a8a7-fc42-4711-9188-75e211a0a7af",
    "timeStamp": "2025-10-13T04:40:44.974216619Z",
    "deploymentPackageId": "01e240ed-c16f-4ab5-b2ab-c138adcd87cd",
    "elapsedTime": 1672,
    "results": [
        {
            "attribute": "RequestAttributes.DivisionId",
            "value": "a39d00a7-8710-4333-adbf-bb82e8c9bacf",
            "decision": "PERMIT",
            "statements": [
                {
                    "id": "d4aa185e-7e51-4e03-af8f-4e8efd03b18a",
