<h3 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-DownstreamAPIInfo(Feb2026ERMdivisionschanges)"=
>Downstream API Info(Feb 2026 ERM divisions changes)</h3>
<ul>
<li>The following PDP Query API will be called only if accountID is supplie=
d as part of the request(with no divisionId). This is to ensure, we can fil=
ter only the specific payments associated with the divisions the user is en=
titled to, refer to the sequence flow here for details: <span style=3D"colo=
r: rgb(255,0,0);"><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/=
ARTC/SD%3A+Sub-Orgs%28Divisions%29+Channels#SD:SubOrgs(Divisions)Channels-P=
aymentstatus-Sentforprocessing" rel=3D"nofollow">SD: Sub-Orgs(Divisions) Ch=
annels - Paymentstatus-Sentforprocessing</a></span>.&nbsp;=20
<ul>
<li>PDPQueryAPI to be uplifted:<span>&nbsp;</span><code>GetDivisionsFromPdp=
QueryResult</code></li>
<li>PDPQueryAPI Request:</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "query": [
        {
            "attribute": "RequestAttributes.DivisionId"
        }
    ],
    "context": {
        "action": "QUERY",
        "attributes": {
            "RequestAttributes.CustomerUserId": "07a975e0-0a90-4e1c-96d1-c2=
a1e5dcc5a2",
            "RequestAttributes.OrganisationId": "32896172",
            "RequestAttributes.RequestAction": "VIEW_PAYMENT"
        }
    }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<ul>
<li>PDPQuery API response:</li>
</ul>
