<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current">FEB 26</spa=
n> <u><strong>Division feature changes:</strong></u> As part of the divisio=
ns feature update, a new request body parameter <code>divisionId</code> has=
 been introduced. If provided, the endpoint will use it to fetch beneficiar=
y IDs via the <code>GetBeneficiaryIdsFromPdpQueryResult</code> API. If not =
provided, the existing logic remains unchanged.</p>
