<h3 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-10.3InputValidation">10.3 Input Validation</h3=
>
<p>The below validations should be done on the extracted account IDs.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 47.=
3727%;" data-snooker-col-series=3D"numbers" data-snooker-locked-cols=3D"0">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 4.95417%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 25.625%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 21.0125%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 48.341%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTh" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false"><br></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Scenario</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Action</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Comment</th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" contenteditable=3D"false" data-m=
ce-resize=3D"false">1</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Either beneficiary id or account id needs to be =
provided&nbsp;</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Return 400</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Return errors if both are empty or both with val=
ues.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<h3 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-10.4Downstreamchanges(aspartofFeb2026divisionf=
eature)">10.4 Downstream changes(as part of <span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0=
,0);">Feb 2026 division feature</span>)</h3>
<p>If <code>divisionId</code> is included in the request body, the endpoint=
 will pass it to the <code>GetBeneficiaryIdsFromPdpQueryResult</code> API t=
o retrieve beneficiary IDs specific to that division, following request bod=
y will come into play when calling <code>GetBeneficiaryIdsFromPdpQueryResul=
t</code> API with divisions. Please note: There will be no change in the <c=
ode>GetBeneficiaryIdsFromPdpQueryResult </code>API response, the response p=
ayload structure will continue to remain the same.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom">
<b class=3D"code-title"></b><span class=3D"collapse-source expand-control" =
style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</sp=
an><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand source</span></span><span cla=
ss=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Midnig=
ht">{
    "query": [
        {
            "attribute": "RequestAttributes.BeneficiaryId"
        }
    ],
    "context": {
        "action": "QUERY",
        "attributes": {
            "RequestAttributes.CustomerUserId": "07a975e0-0a90-4e1c-96d1-c2=
a1e5dcc5a2",
            "RequestAttributes.OrganisationId": "32896172",
            "RequestAttributes.DivisionId": "a39d00a7-8710-4333-adbf-bb82e8=
c9bacf",
            "RequestAttributes.RequestAction": "INITIATE_PAYMENT"
        }
    }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br>
 And if&nbsp;<code>divisionId</code> is not provided in the request body, t=
he endpoint will follow the existing logic.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-11.Capability:Generatepaymentidentifier(paymen=
treference)forasinglecredittransferpayment"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,10=
2,255);"><strong>11. Capability:<span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"> Gen=
erate payment identifier(payment reference) for a single credit transfer pa=
yment</span></strong></span></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/generatePaymentIdentifier"><span>GET /gene=
rateP<span style=3D"color: rgb(33,33,33);">aymentIdentifier</span></span></=
h2>
<p>This endpoint generates the payment identifier(payment reference) for a =
single credit transfer payment. This Exp API route in-turn will consume <em=
 style=3D"text-align: left;">customer-payment-instruction-id-v1</em><em sty=
le=3D"text-align: left;">&nbsp;</em>API<em>(</em>GET /generate route) to ge=
nerate the payment identifier(payment reference).</p>
<h3 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-11.1.Request">11.1. Request</h3>
<p>&nbsp;Query string parameters</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 52.=
5106%;">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 16.4863%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 11.4136%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 26.0997%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 46.0004%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Name</str=
ong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Required<=
/strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Values</s=
trong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Descripti=
on</strong></p></th>
