<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-12.Capability:Retrievethepaymentlimitsapplicab=
leaspartofpaymentworkflowrequestapproval(Nov2025ERM)"><span style=3D"color:=
 rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>12. Capability:<span class=3D"fabric-text-color-=
mark"> Retrieve the payment limits applicable as part of payment workflow r=
equest approval<span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);">(Nov 2025 ERM)</span></=
span></strong></span></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/paymentLimits"><span>GET /paymentLimits</s=
pan></h2>
<p>This endpoint will retrieve the following payment limits applicable as p=
art of payment workflow request approval</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Remaining cumulative Limits for an User(checker) and Organisation Ch=
annel</p></li>
<li>Cumulative limits for an User(checker) and Organisation Channel</li>
<li>Transactional limits for an User(checker)</li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-12.1.Request">12.1. Request</h3>
<p><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"e1069d78-4c58-461b-90e=
d-1759e1d0cbeb">Query Parameters : NA</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>&nbsp;Request Body</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 52.=
5106%;">
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 16.4863%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 11.4136%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 26.0997%;">
<col class=3D"" style=3D"width: 46.0004%;">
</colgroup>
<tbody class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Name</str=
ong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Required<=
/strong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Values</s=
trong></p></th>
<th style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTh"><p><strong>Descripti=
on</strong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">NA</span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>:cross:</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>This will be a GET route and no request body will be required. However, =
when calling Payment Limits CAP API, an appropriate request body will have =
to be constructed(as mentioned in the "Description" column)</p>
<p><br></p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p>The following request body will have to be constructed in the Exp API wh=
en calling Payment Limits CAP API(this request will fetch the user, organis=
ation channel and scheme limit rules for a specific user under a specific o=
rganisation)</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: sql; gutter: false; theme: Midnight" data-theme=3D"Midnight">{
 &nbsp;  "userCISKey": "123456",
    "organisationCISKey": "org12345678"
    "channelId": "A014A6"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p>Payment Limits CAP API will accept the following request body attributes=
</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable" data-mce-resize=3D"false">
<colgroup>
<col>
<col>
<col>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Field</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><pre>level</pre></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>string</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-align: left;">Accepted Enum val=
ues</p>
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li>User</li>
<li>organisationChannel</li>
<li>SchemeChannel</li>
</ul><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p><p style=3D"text-align: left;">=
For user and organisationChannel limit level, both transactional and cumula=
tive limit will be returned.</p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p><p s=
tyle=3D"text-align: left;">For Channels requirement, this attribute need no=
t be passed as part of the request body</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">userCIS=
Key</span></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Fetch user's CISKey from <span style=3D"color=
: rgb(23,43,77);">apiHeaders['x-userId']</span></p><p>RegEx: <span class=3D=
"sc-dChVcU sc-izQBue ehybzg jozLIs" style=3D"color: rgb(102,102,102);">stri=
ng</span><span class=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-jBeBSR ehybzg iRpqdy" style=3D"color: =
rgb(102,102,102);"><span>&nbsp;</span>(UserCISKey)<span>&nbsp;</span></span=
><span class=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-fscmHZ ehybzg gxHEql">&lt;=3D 100 characters<s=
pan>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-cTTdyq ehybzg hoLLjT" s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(14,124,134);">^[0-9A-Za-z]{1,100}$</span></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">organisati=
onCISKey</span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Fetch Organisation CISKey from protected requ=
est header "protected-orgId"</p><p>RegEx: <span class=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-izQBu=
e ehybzg jozLIs" style=3D"color: rgb(102,102,102);">string</span><span clas=
s=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-jBeBSR ehybzg iRpqdy" style=3D"color: rgb(102,102,102);">=
<span>&nbsp;</span>(OrganisationCISKey)<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span clas=
s=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-fscmHZ ehybzg gxHEql">&lt;=3D 100 characters<span>&nbsp;<=
/span></span><span class=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-cTTdyq ehybzg hoLLjT" style=3D"col=
or: rgb(14,124,134);">^[0-9A-Za-z]{1,100}$</span></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">channelId<=
/span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li>AlfabetId of the channel that the organisation belongs to&nbsp;</li>
<li>Mandatory to retrieve the organisation channel limit</li>
</ul><p>Read OriginatingSystemID(AlfabetId) from x-Originatingsystemid requ=
est header and assign it to "channel" attribute</p><p>RegEx: string (Channe=
lId) &lt;=3D 100 characters ^[A-Za-z0-9._-]+$</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">scheme</sp=
an></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-align: left;">Accepted Enum val=
ues</p>
<ul style=3D"text-align: left;">
<li>NPP</li>
<li>DE</li>
</ul><p><br></p><p>For Channels requirement, this attribute need not be pas=
sed as part of the request body</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><span styl=
e=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">currencyCode</span></span></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">string</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><span class=3D"sc=
-dChVcU sc-izQBue ehybzg jozLIs" style=3D"color: rgb(102,102,102);">string<=
/span><span>&nbsp;<span class=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-fscmHZ ehybzg gxHEql">=3D 3 c=
haracters&nbsp;</span></span><span class=3D"sc-dChVcU sc-cTTdyq ehybzg hoLL=
jT" style=3D"color: rgb(14,124,134);">^[A-Z]{3}$</span></p><p style=3D"text=
-align: left;">Default: "AUD"</p><p style=3D"text-align: left;"><br></p><p =
style=3D"text-align: left;">For Channels requirement(for MVP), this attribu=
te need not be passed as part of the request body as the currency will be d=
efaulted to AUD</p></td>
