<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-13.Capability:Validatepaymentlimitsaspartofpay=
mentworkflowrequestapproval(Nov2025ERM)"><strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(=
51,102,255);">13. Capability:</span><span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">=
<span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"> Validate payment limits as part of=
 payment workflow request approval</span><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0)=
;">(Nov 2025 ERM)</span></span></strong></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-POST/validatePaymentLimits"><span>POST /valida=
tePaymentLimits</span></h2>
<p>This endpoint will validate the following payment limits applicable as p=
art of the payment workflow request approval. Also, this route will deduct =
the user's and organisation channel cumulative limits if the limits are not=
 reached yet.</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Cumulative Limits for an User(checker) and Organisation Channel</p><=
/li>
<li>Transactional limits for an User(checker)</li>
<li>Other limits: DE Market limit (transactional limit) &amp; NPP Market li=
mit (transactional limit)</li>
</ul>
