<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-16.Capability:BSBlooksupforbankname"><span sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>16.&nbsp;<span class=3D"fabric-text-=
color-mark"> </span></strong></span><strong style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255)=
;letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Capability:<span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark=
"> BSB looks up for bank name</span></strong></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/bsbLookup"><span>GET /<span style=3D"color=
: rgb(23,43,77);">bsbLookup</span></span></h2>
<p>This endpoint triggers the INF API (<a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.=
au/components/apis/inf-bnkng-chnl-brchntwk-v2?tab=3Dcontract#tag/BranchRefe=
renceData/operation/getBranchReferenceData" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"=
nofollow">inf-bnkng-chnl-brchntwk-v2 - APIs - Components - Mesh Connect</a>=
) getBranchReferenceData method to <span>return bank name based on the BSB =
provided by the users.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span>( The endpoint needs to be uplifted with the bank name in the payl=
oad )</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-334494380" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-334494380" cl=
