0" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expa=
nded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-334494380"><span class=3D"e=
xpand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=
=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Deta=
ils of retrieving the list of arrangements</span></button>
</div>
