<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-17.Capability:RetrievingAccountListfromPDP(Nov=
2025ERM)"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>17.&nbsp;<span cl=
ass=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"> </span></strong></span><strong style=3D"col=
or: rgb(51,102,255);letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Capability:<span class=3D"fab=
ric-text-color-mark">&nbsp;Retrieving Account List from PDP(Nov 2025 ERM)</=
span></strong></h1>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/accountList"><span>GET /</span>accountList=
</h2>
<p>This endpoint retrieves all accounts from PDP(Entitlements) that the use=
r is entitled to view. And if an account group id is supplied, the endpoint=
 will retrieve all accounts from PDP(Entitlements) the user is entitled to =
view for the supplied account ID.<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=3D"color: r=
gb(255,0,0);"><u><strong>Note:<span>&nbsp;</span></strong></u>This endpoint=
 will only query PDP to retrieve the account list as held in entitlements a=
nd will not make any call to the Westpac One Core Arrangements CAP API to r=
etrieve the details from either 10x/Atlas or GCM.</span></p>
<p>This endpoint will be called in the following flows,</p>
<ul>
<li>BR.03 requirement in this SD:<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=3D"https://conf=
luence.srv.westpac.com.au/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D2041141342#SD:Upli=
ftmaximumloadsizefordifferentlistings&amp;warnuserwhenmorerecordsareavailab=
le-SolutionOverview" rel=3D"nofollow">SD : Uplift maximum load size for dif=
ferent listings &amp; warn user when more records are available#SolutionOve=
rview</a></li>
<li>Feb 2026 ERM divisions SD: <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.co=
m.au/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=3D2117707286#SD:SubOrgs(Divisions)Channel=
s-MakeaPayment/Transferfunds" rel=3D"nofollow">SD: Sub-Orgs(Divisions) Chan=
nels - MakeaPayment/Transferfunds</a></li>
<li>Feb 2026 ERM divisions SD: <a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.co=
m.au/display/ARTC/SD%3A+Sub-Orgs%28Divisions%29+Channels#SD:SubOrgs(Divisio=
ns)Channels-Paymentstatus-Sentforprocessing" rel=3D"nofollow">SD: Sub-Orgs(=
Divisions) Channels - Paymentstatus-Sentforprocessing</a></li>
</ul>
<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<div id=3D"expander-286866531" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-286866531" cl=
ass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-28686653=
1" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-expa=
nded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-286866531"><span class=3D"e=
xpand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hidden=
=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">Deta=
ils for retrieving the account list</span></button>
</div>
<div role=3D"region" id=3D"expander-content-286866531" class=3D"expand-cont=
ent" aria-labelledby=3D"expand-button-286866531">
