<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: -0.006em;"><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,4=
3,77);">And if <code>divisionId</code><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"=
><span>&nbsp;</span>is not provided in the request body, the endpoint will =
follow the existing logic.</span></span></span></p>
