<p><br></p>
<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-18.Capability:Checkifbeneficiaryisupdated/arch=
ived"><strong style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);font-size: 24.0px;letter-spac=
ing: -0.01em;">18. Capability:<span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"> Check=
 if beneficiary is updated/archived</span></strong></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-POST/verifyBeneficiary"><span>POST /<span styl=
e=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">verifyBeneficiary</span></span></h2>
<p>This endpoint compares account object by retrieving latest account detai=
l with the "id" in the payload, return true if beneficiary is changed or ar=
chived.</p>
<p>Step:</p>
<ol>
<li>call the Beneficiary INF API with the beneficiary id supplied in the re=
quest.</li>
<li>if the status is ARCHIVE, return true anyway, otherwise;</li>
<li>compare "account/bsb/PayID" from the response against the request paylo=
ad.&nbsp;</li>
<li>if the data does not match, return true in the response payload.</li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
