<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-19.Capability:Toretrievedivisionsunderanorgani=
sationfortheloggedinuser"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>1=
9. Capability:<span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"> To retrieve divisions=
 under an organisation for the logged in user</span></strong></span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/divisionList"><span>GET /<span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(23,43,77);">divisionList</span></span></h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">This endpoint retrieves the list o=
f divisions under an organisation for the logged in user</span></p>
<p>Step:</p>
<ol>
<li>The endpoint will query PDP to retrieve the divisions based on OrgCISKe=
y and logged in user's CISKey</li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<p>This endpoint will be used in the following flows:&nbsp;</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/SD%3A+Sub=
-Orgs%28Divisions%29+Channels#SD:SubOrgs(Divisions)Channels-MakeaPayment/Tr=
ansferfunds" rel=3D"nofollow">SD: Sub-Orgs(Divisions) Channels - MakeaPayme=
nt/Transferfunds</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/SD%3A+Sub=
-Orgs%28Divisions%29+Channels#SD:SubOrgs(Divisions)Channels-Paymentstatus-S=
entforprocessing" rel=3D"nofollow">SD: Sub-Orgs(Divisions) Channels - Payme=
ntstatus-Sentforprocessing</a></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
