<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-20.Capability:Tovalidatetheconfirmationofpayee=
namewhenmakingapaymenttoanewBSBandaccountnobeneficiary(May2026ERM)"><span s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>20. Capability:<span class=3D"fabr=
ic-text-color-mark"> </span></strong></span><strong style=3D"color: rgb(51,=
102,255);letter-spacing: -0.01em;"><span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">T=
o validate the confirmation of payee name when making a payment to a new BS=
B and account no beneficiary (May 2026 ERM)</span></strong></h1>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-POST/accountNameCheck"><span>POST /accountName=
Check</span></h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">This endpoint validates the custom=
er name for both, On-Us or Off-us scenarios.</span></p>
<p>Integration/Orchestration:<span>&nbsp;</span><span>The endpoint will con=
sume the following APIs,</span></p>
<ol>
<li>The CoP Daily limit and Session limit static values will be configured =
and maintained in the EXP API config</li>
<li><p><strong>channel-payment-utils-v1 API</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><code>GET /payment/counters/{name}/customers/{customerId}</code><br>
 =E2=86=92 Used to validate whether the CoP daily limit has reached for a u=
ser.</li>
<li><code>GET /payment/counters/{name}/customers/sessions/{sessionId}</code=
><br>
 =E2=86=92 Used to validate whether the CoP session limit has reached for a=
 user.</li>
<li><code>POST /payment/counters/{name}/customers/{customerId}/sessions/{se=
ssionId}</code><br>
 =E2=86=92 Used to increment the CoP daily counter &amp; session counter if=
 the limits have not yet been reached.</li>
<li><code>POST /payment/counters/{name}/customers/{customerId}</code><br>
 =E2=86=92 Used to increment the CoP daily counter if the limits have not y=
et been reached.</li>
</ul></li>
<li><p><strong>payee-services-v1 API</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><code>POST /accountNameCheck</code><br>
 =E2=86=92 Used to validate the payee name as part of the CoP process.</li>
</ul></li>
<li><strong>Send Custom Fact("PAYEE_NAME_CHECK_COLOUR") to SAFI</strong>
<ul>
<li>Custom fact to SAFI will go via <em>cap-custsvcmgt-custsecyverifctn-ada=
ptvauth-v2</em> CAP API <em>POST /analyse</em> endpoint <s>Entitlements usi=
ng "mep-node/framework-otp-provider-addon" MESH JS Library</s>.<s> Implemen=
tation reference can be found here:&nbsp;<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D=
"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/WDP/repos/galaxy-beneficiary=
-microfrontend/browse/api/server/api/controllers/postAliasLookupController.=
ts?at=3Drefs%2Fheads%2Ffeature%2FART-58608-safi-payid-lookup-2#112" rel=3D"=
nofollow">Source of postAliasLookupController.ts - safi-payid-lookup-2#112<=
/a></s></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">This endpoint will be used in the =
following flow: </span><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/dis=
play/ARTC/06+-+SD%3A+Confirmation+of+payee" rel=3D"nofollow">06 - SD: Confi=
rmation of payee</a></p>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-504467909" class=3D"expand-container">
