<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;The endpoint wil=
l retrieve the user's CoP daily limit counter</strong></p>
<ul>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">
