</div>
</div>
<p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The endpoint will incr=
ement the user's CoP daily limit counter</strong>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">&nbsp;Increment daily counter reques=
t: POST inf/channel/payment/utils/v1/payment/counters/{<strong>name</strong=
>}/customers/{<strong>customerId</strong>}</span>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">name =3D CoP</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">customerId =3D userId of the logged =
in user</span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Increment daily counter response:&nb=
sp;</span></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
