<p><br></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Send Custom Fact("PAYEE_NAME_CHECK_COLOUR") to SAFI</strong>&nb=
sp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>To send the custom fact to SAFI, Channels will consume <em style=3D"let=
ter-spacing: 0.0px;">cap-custsvcmgt-custsecyverifctn-adaptvauth-v2</em><spa=
n style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;"> CAP API </span><em style=3D"letter-spac=
ing: 0.0px;">POST /analyse</em><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;"> endp=
oint(<a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/cap-custsvcmgt-=
custsecyverifctn-adaptvauth-v2?tab=3Dcontract#tag/Analyse/operation/analyse=
" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">cap-custsvcmgt-custsecyverifctn-=
adaptvauth-v2 - POST /analyse</a>)</span><s style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;=
">use the MESH JS library (<strong><code>mep-node/framework-otp-provider-ad=
don</code></strong>), specifically the&nbsp;<strong><code>OtpProvider.analy=
se</code></strong>&nbsp;function, which transmits custom fact details to SA=
FI via Entitlements</s><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">.<s> Please r=
efer to the implementation here for further details:</s></span><s><span sty=
le=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">&nbsp;</span><a class=3D"external-link" style=
=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;" href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/pr=
ojects/WDP/repos/galaxy-beneficiary-microfrontend/browse/api/server/api/con=
trollers/postAliasLookupController.ts?at=3Drefs%2Fheads%2Ffeature%2FART-586=
08-safi-payid-lookup#133" rel=3D"nofollow">Source of postAliasLookupControl=
ler.ts - safi-payid-lookup#133</a></s>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">CAP API Request Body</span>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">For "eventType", d</span>epending on=
 where in the flow a bene can be added/updated, one of the following should=
 be set=20
<ul>
<li><span>ADD_PAYEE-BENEFICIARY</span></li>
<li><span>EDIT_PAYEE-BENEFICIARY</span><span>&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span>PAYMENT</span></li>
</ul></li>
<li><span>"eventMetaData" object will be constructed as below,</span></li>
<li>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
