><strong style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">value(one of the below based on C=
oP response)</strong></pre></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><pre><span><strong>eventMetaData.</strong></span=
><strong style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">datatype</strong></pre></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span>PAYEE_NAME_CHECK_COLOUR&nbsp;</span><sp=
an style=3D"color: rgb(205,89,55);"><em>&nbsp;</em></span></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span><em>Blue</em> =E2=80=93 if matched</spa=
n></p><p><span><em>Amber</em> =E2=80=93 not complete match/be cautious</spa=
n></p><p><span><em>Red</em> =E2=80=93 no match</span></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p><span><em>String</em></span></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
