<h1 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-Capability:ReferenceDataforInternationalPaymen=
t"><strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capability: Refe=
rence Data for International Payment</strong></span></strong></h1>
<p><strong><br></strong></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/referenceData/countryList"><strong><span>G=
ET /referenceData/countryList</span></strong></h2>
<p><strong>This API retrieves a list of countries currently supported by W1=
T for user to select when making international payment or creating internat=
ional beneficiary. It also returns a scenario index for the front end to de=
termine which combination of fields to display for a particular country (1=
=3DIBAN mandatory, 2=3DNCC mandatory, 3=3DNCC optional, 4=3DSWIFT/BIC only)=
.</strong></p>
