<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/referenceData/currencyList"><strong><span>=
GET /referenceData/currencyList</span></strong></h2>
<p><strong>This API retrieves a list of currencies supported for the select=
ed country, for user to select when making an international payment or crea=
ting an international beneficiary. Filtered to only return currencies curre=
ntly supported by W1T.</strong></p>
