<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/referenceData/bankDetailList"><strong><spa=
n>GET /referenceData/bankDetailList</span></strong></h2>
<p><strong>This API retrieves a list of bank details (SWIFT/BIC code, bank =
