<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/referenceData/bankDetailListByNCC"><strong=
><span>GET /referenceData/bankDetailListByNCC</span></strong></h2>
<p><strong>This API retrieves a list of bank details by NCC (National Clear=
ing Code) identifier for a specific country. Searches by partial branch ide=
ntifier (e.g. ABA for US, CNAPS for CN). Used during international payment =
initiation or beneficiary creation to look up bank details by country-speci=
fic clearing code.</strong></p>
<p><strong><br></strong></p>
