<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/referenceData/cutoffList"><strong><span>GE=
T /referenceData/cutoffList</span></strong></h2>
<p><strong>This API retrieves the earliest cut-off time for a given country=
 and currency combination to display as a warning to users during payment i=
nitiation. The API returns the earliest (minimum) cut-off time by comparing=
 values from the country_cutoff and currency_cutoff tables.</strong></p>
<p><strong><br></strong></p>
