<h2 id=3D"expgalaxypaymentv2-GET/referenceData/purposeCodeList"><strong><sp=
an>GET /referenceData/purposeCodeList</span></strong></h2>
<p><strong>This API retrieves a list of purpose codes and their description=
s for a given country, to be displayed in the 'Reason of Payment' dropdown =
during international payment initiation.</strong></p>
<p><strong><br></strong></p>
